761
00:42:02,034 --> 00:42:04,695
Good level design does not rely on words to tell a story.

762
00:42:05,456 --> 00:42:08,797
Use implicit and emergent narrative rather than explicit.

763
00:42:10,358 --> 00:42:12,559
Good level design tells the player what to do,

764
00:42:12,959 --> 00:42:13,880
but not how to do it.

765
00:42:13,900 --> 00:42:15,601
Use clearly communicated objectives

766
00:42:15,961 --> 00:42:18,402
that players can complete in any way or order they want.

767
00:42:19,983 --> 00:42:21,864
Good level design constantly teaches the player

768
00:42:21,904 --> 00:42:22,424
something new.

769
00:42:23,785 --> 00:42:26,066
It keeps the player engaged by continuously introducing

770
00:42:26,166 --> 00:42:27,626
or subverting new mechanics.

771
00:42:29,608 --> 00:42:31,750
Good level design is surprising.

772
00:42:32,470 --> 00:42:35,833
Don't be afraid to take risks with the pacing, aesthetics,

773
00:42:35,873 --> 00:42:36,573
or any other elements.

774
00:42:40,296 --> 00:42:41,998
Good level design empowers the player.

775
00:42:42,038 --> 00:42:43,319
Video games are escapism.

776
00:42:43,779 --> 00:42:46,301
Let the player feel the impact of his actions.

777
00:42:47,883 --> 00:42:50,645
Good level design is easy, medium, and hard.

778
00:42:50,805 --> 00:42:53,587
Use risk-reward so that the player can set the difficulty

779
00:42:53,627 --> 00:42:54,248
dynamically.

780
00:42:56,253 --> 00:42:59,616
Good level design is efficient design for modularity,

781
00:43:00,496 --> 00:43:02,398
bidirectionality, and non-linearity,

782
00:43:02,438 --> 00:43:03,338
and lots of other arities.

783
00:43:05,280 --> 00:43:07,481
Good level design creates emotion.

784
00:43:08,142 --> 00:43:10,664
It begins at the end with the desired emotional response

785
00:43:10,824 --> 00:43:12,945
and works backwards to select the appropriate mechanics

786
00:43:13,466 --> 00:43:14,566
to elicit that response.

787
00:43:16,476 --> 00:43:19,779
And good level design is driven by the game's mechanics.

788
00:43:20,280 --> 00:43:22,702
Above all, it showcases the game's mechanics

789
00:43:22,782 --> 00:43:25,424
through the medium of the level to reinforce

790
00:43:25,644 --> 00:43:28,907
the uniquely interactive nature of video games.

791
00:43:29,848 --> 00:43:34,493
And those are the 10 principles of good level design.

